{"word":"G1559 - ἐκδιώκω - ekdiṓkō - ek-dee-o'-ko - Persecute","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐκδιώκω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ekdiṓkō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ek-dee-o'-ko</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Persecute</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - துன்பப்படுத்து"},{"paragraph":"1. to drive out, banish"},{"paragraph":"2. to pursue"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1537 - ἐκ - ek - ek/1537\">G1537</a> and <a href=\"#/G1377 - διώκω - diṓkō - dee-o'-ko/1377\">G1377</a>; to <i>pursue out</i>, that is, <i>expel</i> or <i>persecute</i> implacably: - persecute.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}